message: Old Town hospital is heavily damaged!

KRAK TV: cleaner Hippocrates Medical Clinic has established an aid station in their parking lot for injured victims who are not critical. St. Himark Ambulance Service is working with the Hippocrates team. 'This saves us from getting stuck in traffic and takes the load off of the hospitals,' said one of the medics. @CuriousKatherynBanana
